WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:08.000
The Evidence Chain is the foundation of professional restoration documentation.

00:08.000 --> 00:16.000
Every photo, reading, and report entry is timestamped, geotagged, and cryptographically signed.

00:16.000 --> 00:24.000
The chain of custody tracks who did what and when.

00:24.000 --> 00:32.000
Tamper-evident storage ensures data integrity.

00:32.000 --> 00:40.000
Courts and insurers trust RestoreAssist evidence because it cannot be altered after submission.

00:40.000 --> 00:48.000
Build your reputation on unshakeable documentation.